      "cookedHtml": "<p>Now that you learned all about our 2024 vision of the exciting new features and enhancements planned for our products, we want to hear from you!</p>\n<p><strong>What Elevate '23 announcement are you most excited about for 2024!</strong></p>\n<div class=\"poll\">\n<div class=\"poll-container\"><ul>\n<li>mondayDB</li>\n<li>Standardization toolkit</li>\n<li>Next generation of boards</li>\n<li>Enterprise improvement</li>\n<li>monday products</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"poll-info\">\n<div class=\"poll-info_counts\">\n<div class=\"poll-info_counts-count\">\n<span class=\"info-number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"info-label\">voters</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><strong>If you didn’t have a chance to tune into Elevate '23 live, you can still watch all the sessions and more <a href=\"https://monday.com/elevate\">here.</a></strong></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/8/583c86a63c46619f1c7c4a8ee99c103d7db4d816.jpeg\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-12-14 at 15.44.38\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/8/583c86a63c46619f1c7c4a8ee99c103d7db4d816_2_690x386.jpeg\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-12-14 at 15.44.38\" width=\"690\" height=\"386\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-12-14 at 15.44.38</span><span class=\"informations\">1864×1044 98.1 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/4/84d750b3a14c1cb0581d8f42a133f0505ccf9eb8.jpeg\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-12-14 at 15.44.29\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/4/84d750b3a14c1cb0581d8f42a133f0505ccf9eb8_2_690x394.jpeg\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-12-14 at 15.44.29\" width=\"690\" height=\"394\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-12-14 at 15.44.29</span><span class=\"informations\">1898×1084 82.7 K